metadata.description: The Shadow token is the native token of Shadow Drive. Shadow Drive is the only decentralized data storage platform native to the Solana ecosystem that provides immutable decentralized permanent data storage without sacrificing performance. Files are uploaded to Shadow Drive using the Shdw Token. Shdw Tokens used to pay for file storage are burned and removed from supply. The Shdw Token has a fixed total supply and total supply decreases as Shadow Drive user adoption grows.
